data.text:
b. 1 February 1894, Cape Elizabeth, Maine, USA

d. 31 August 1973, Palm Desert, California, USA. (cancer)

John Wayne Movies he Directed:

Stagecoach, They Were Expendable, Fort Apache, 3 Godfathers, She wore a Yellow Ribbon, Rio Grande, The Quiet Man, The Searchers, The Wings of Eagles, The Horse Soldiers, The Man who shot Liberty Valance, How the west was won, Donovan’s reef, Chesty: A Tribute to a Legend.
